{"title":"最新最美的画面","authors":["高云"],"dates":[{"year":1960,"month":5,"day":4}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"最新最美的画面"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大连造船厂　高云"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自动线，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自动线……像天上的银河，像山涧的清泉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——一条玉带，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"横划车间。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"工件汇成河流，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"滚滚向前。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钢的——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"银光夺目，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铜的——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金光灿烂。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金波银浪在翻腾，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金银河畔好喜欢。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"徒弟——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在欢笑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"师傅——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在赞叹。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唱吧，跳吧！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"车间出现长流水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——永远是春天！自动线，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自动线……一条精美的银链，一条奇异的琴弦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它在叮当作响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"弹动着我们的心弦。我们在操纵台上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"按动着电钮；我们在自动线旁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"巡回着车间。台台机床，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"宛如蓝色的宝石；自动线哪它就是"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"贯穿宝石的银线。东面——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"原料成堆，西面——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"产品成山。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"前面是，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"朝霞映红的大道，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"前面是，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"瑰丽庄严的宫殿……自动线哪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自动线，党的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金色光芒——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是你的经丝，群众的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无穷智慧——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是你的纬线，织成了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"织成了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"最新最美的画面！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}